title: Guest Co-Host Nur-d Joins Us Today
description: The dumbest thing a customer has asked you, Nur-d joins the show to guest co-host and we talk about the first time you felt like an adult, an update from Lauren from yesterday who found something suspicious on a co-workers computer, an update from last week's Group Therpay plus a new one about someone's husband wanting to put in a putting green in their backyard, Nur-d tries to get his friend to Venmo him $250, and more!
